hadiths[27]{hadithnumber,text}:
3743,"Sahal-bin-Sad Saaidi (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai Uwemir Ajlani (Raziallahu anhu), Aasim bin Adi Ansari (Raziallahu anhu) ke paas aaya aur unse kaha aey Aasim ! bhala agar koi shakhs apni joru ke sath kisi mard ko dekhey kya usko mar daaley, phir tum usko mar dalogey ya wo kya karey? to ye masla poochho mere waastey Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se. Aasim (Raziallahu anhu) ne Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se puchha aap ne is qism ke sawaalon ko na-pasand kya aur unki burai bayan ki. Aasim (Raziallahu anhu) ne jo Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se suna wo unko sakht guzra . jab wo apne logon mein lot kar aaey to Uwemir (Raziallahu anhu) unke paas aaey aur puchha aey Aasim! janabe-Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne kya farmaaya? Aasim (Raziallahu anhu) ne Uwemir (Raziallahu anhu) se kaha to mere liye achi cheez nahi laya. Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko tera masla poochhna na-gawar hua. Uwemir (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha qism khuda ki main to baaz na aaunga jab tak ye masla aap se na poochhunga. phir Uwemir (Raziallahu anhu) aaey Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke paas tamam logon main aur arz kya ya Rasulullah ! aap kya farmatey hain agar koi shakhs apni bevi ke paas ghair mard ko dekhey usko mar daaley, phir aap usko mar daalengey (iske qisaas mein) wo kya karey? Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya terey aur teri joru ke baab mein Allah ka hukm utra (yani aayate-liaan ki) to ja aur apni bevi ko lekar aa. Sehal (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha phir donon miyan bevi ne liaan kya aur main logon ke sath Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke paas maujood tha jab wo farigh huey to Uwemir (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha ya Rasulullah agar main us aurat ko ab rakhun to main jhoota hun phir Uwemir (Raziallahu anhu) ne usko teen talaaq de din is se pahley ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) usko hukm kartey ibne-Shahab ne kaha phir liaan karne walon ka yahi tariqa thehar gaya."
3744,Sahal-bin-Sad (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai Uwemir Ansari (Raziallahu anhu) jo bani Ajlan mein se tha Aasim bin Adi (Raziallahu anhu) ke paas aaya phir bayan kya hadis ko akheer tak isi tarah jaisey uper guzri aur hadis mein ibne-Shahab ka qaul bhi Sharik kar diya ke phir judai mard ko aurat se sunnat ho gaee liaan karne walon main aur itna zyada kya ke Sehal ne kaha wo aurat haamla thi iske betey ko maa ki taraf nisbat karke pukaartey phir ye tariqa jari hua ke aisa ladka apni maan ka waaris hoga aur wo uski waaris hogi apne hissey ke muwafiq .
3745,ibne-Juraij se riwayat hai ke mujh se ibne-Shahab ne bayan kya mutlaaeneen (Liaan karnewaley) ka haal aur unka tariqa Sahal-bin-Sad (Raziallahu anhu) ki hadis se jo bani saaida mein se tha usne kaha Ansar mein se aik shakhs Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke paas aaya aur arz kya ya Rasulullah aap kya samajhtey hain agar koi shakhs apni joru ke sath kisi mard ko dekhey aur bayan kya Sara qissa hadis ka aur itna zyada kya ke phir donon ne liaan kya masjid ke andar aur main maujood tha aur is riwayat mein ye bhi hai ke us shakhs ne talaaq di teen baar apni aurat ko Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke hukm karne se pahley phir wo juda ho gaya us se aap ke samney aap ne farmaya yahi judai hai darmyan liaan karne walon ke.
3746,"Saeed-bin-Jubair se riwayat hai mujh se puchha gaya liaan karne walon ka masla Musab bin Zuber ki khilafat mein, main hairan hua kya jawab dun to main chala Abdullah-bin-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) ke makan ki taraf Makka main aur unke ghulam se kaha merey aaney ka zikr karo. usne kaha wo aaraam kartey hain. unhon-ne meri awaz suni aur kaha kya Juber ka betaa hai? maine kaha haan unhon-ne kaha andar aa qism khuda ki to kisi kaam se aaya hoga. main andar aa gaya to wo aik kambal bichhaaey baithey they aur aik takiye par tek lagaey they jo chhaal se khajoor ki bhara hua tha. maine kaha aey abu-Abdur-Rehman ! liaan karne walon mein judai ki jaeygi ? unhon-ne kaha Subhan-Allah beshak judai ki jaeygi aur sabse pahley is baab mein falan ne puchha jo falan ka betaa tha Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se. usne kaha ya Rasulullah aap kya samajhtey hain agar ham mein se koi apni aurat ko bura kaam karatey dekhey to kya karey, agar munh se nikaley to buri baat nikalega agar chup rahe to aisi buri baat se kyonkar chup rahe ? Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ye sun kar chup ho rahe aur jawab nahi diya. phir wo shakhs aap ke paas aaya aur kehney laga, ya Rasulullah. jo baat maine aap se poochhi thi main khud usmein pad gaya. tab Allah Taala ne ye aayatein utaarin sura Noor mein) والذین یرمون ازواجھم ( aakhir tak. aap ne ye aayatein mard ko padh kar sunain aur usko nasihat ki aur samjhaaya ke duniya ka azab aakhirat ke azab se aasan hai. (yani agar to jhoot bohtan baandhta hai to ab bhi bol de, hade-qazaf ke assi kode pad jaeinge, magar ye jahannam mein jalney se aasan hai). wo bola nahi qism uski jisne aapko sachchaai ke sath bheja maine aurat par bohtan nahi joda . phir aap ne aurat ko bulaya aur usko daraaya aur samjhaya aur farmaya duniya ka azab Sehal hai aakhirat ke azab se. wo boli nahi qism uski jisne aapko sachchaai ke sath bheja hai mera khawind jhoot bolta hai. tab aap ne shuru kya mard se aur us ne char gawahiyan din Allah Taala ke naam ki muqarrar ke wo sachcha hai aur paanchwin baar mein ye kaha ke khuda ki phitkar ho is par agar wo jhoota ho. phir aurat ko bulaya us ne char gawahiyan dein Allah Taala ke naam ki muqarrar ke mard jhoota hai aur paanchwein baar mein ye kaha Allah ka ghazab utrey is par agar mard sachcha hai. iske baad aap ne judai kara di un donon mein."
3747,is sanad se hi mandarja bula riwayat naql ki gaee hai.
3748,"Abdullah-bin-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya liaan karne walon ko , tum donon ka hisab Allah Taala par hai, tum mein se aik jhoota hai. aap ne khawind se farmaya ab tera koi bas aurat par nahi hai kyonke wo tujh se hamesha ke liye juda ho gaee. mard bola mera maal ya Rasulullah ! jo usney liya hai. aap ne farmaya maal tujh ko nahi milega , kyonke agar to sachcha hai to maal ka badla hai jo uski farj tujh par halal ho gaee aur agar to jhoota hai to maal aur door ho gaya ( balke terey uper aur wabaal hua jhoot ka ( . Zuhair ne apni riwayat mein kaha : hamein Sufiyan ne Amr se hadis bayan ki, unhon-ne Saeed-bin-Jubair se suna wo ke rahe they : maine Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) se suna wo keh rahe they : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya."
3749,Abdullah-bin-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne judai kar di bani-Ajlan ki joru aur mard main aur farmaya Allah Taala janta hai tum mein se koi jhoota hai. phir kya tum mein se koi tauba karta hai?
3750,Saeed-bin-Jubair se riwayat hai ke maine ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) se liaan ko puchha to unhon-ne naql kya janab Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se aisa hi jaisey uper guzra.
3751,Saeed-bin-Jubair se riwayat hai Musab ne judai nahi ki liaan karne walon mein. maine iska zikr kya Abdullah-bin-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) se. unhon-ne kaha janab Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne judai kar di bani Ajlan ke mard aur aurat mein.
3752,Abdullah-bin-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke aik mard ne liaan kya Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke zamaney mein phir aap ne judai kar di donon main aur bachchey ka nasb maan se laga diya.
3753,Abdullah-bin-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne liaan karwaya darmyan aik mard Ansari aur uski aurat ke aur judai kar di un donon mein.
3754,wahi jo uper guzra .
3755,"Abdullah-bin-Masood (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai, main Juma ki raat ko masjid mein tha itney mein aik mard Ansari aaya aur bola agar koi apni joru ke paas kisi mard ko paaey aur munh se nikaley to tum usko kode lagaaogey (hade-qazaf ke) agar mar daley to tum usko mar daalogey ( qisaas mein) agar chup rahe to apna ghussa pi kar chup rahe. qism Allah ki main janab Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se poochhunga is masley ko jab doosra din hua to janab Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke paas aaya aur aap se puchha usne kaha agar koi shakhs apni bevi ke sath kisi ko paaey phir munh se nikaley to tum kode lagaaogey agar mar daley to tum usko bhi mar daalogey agar chup rahe to apna ghussa kha kar chup rahe (ye bhi nahi ho sakta ( janab Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya Allah khol de (is mushkil ko) aur dua karne lagey tab liaan ki aayat utri . والذین یرمون ازواجھم ولم یکن لھم shohdaa الا انفسھم . akheer tak phir us mard ka imtihaan liya gaya logon ke samney aur wo uski joru donon Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke paas aaey aur liaan kya pahley mard ne gawahi di char baar ke wo sachcha hai phir paanchwein baar laanat karke kaha agar wo jhoota ho to is par laanat hai khuda taala ki phir aurat chali liaan karne ko aap ne farmaya thehar (aur agar khawind ki baat sach hai to too apne qasoor ka iqrar kar) lekin us ne na maana aur liaan kya jab peeth mod kar chaley to aap ne farmaya us aurat ka bachcha shayad kaley rang ka ghoongariyaley baalon wala paida hoga (us shakhs ki sura par jiska khawind ko guman tha). phir waisa hi kala ghoongariyaley baalon wala paida hua."
3756,Aamash se is sanad ke sath isi tarah manqul hai.
3757,"Muhammad se riwayat hai maine Anas-bin-Malik se puchha ye samajh karke unko malum hai. unhon-ne kaha ke Hilal bin Umayya (Raziallahu anhu) ne nisbat ki zina ki apni biwi ko Sharik bin Sehma se aur Sharik bin Sehma, Bara bin Malik (Raziallahu anhu) ka maa-jaaya bhai tha aur us ( Hilal bin Umayya (Raziallahu anhu)) ne sabse pahley liaan kya Islam mein. rawi ne kaha phir donon miyan biwi ne liaan kya to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya us aurat ko dekhtey raho agar iska bachcha safaid rang ka, seedhey baal waala, laal aankhon wala paida ho to wo Hilal bin Umayya (Raziallahu anhu) ka hai aur jo surmai aankhon waala, ghungariyaley baalon waala, patli pindliyon wala paida ho to wo Sharik bin Sehma ka hai. Anas (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha mujh ko khabar pahunchi ke us aurat ka ladka surmagin aankh, ghungariyaley baal aur patli pindliyon wala paida hua."
3758,"Abdullah-bin-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke paas liaan ka zikr hua. Aasim bin Adi (Raziallahu anhu) ne usmein kuchh kaha phir wo chaley gaey. tab unke paas unki qaum ka aik shakhs aaya aur shikayat karne laga ke usne apni bevi ke sath aik mard ko dekha. Aasim (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha, main us bila mein mubtala hua apni baat ki wjah se. phir Aasim (Raziallahu anhu) usko lekar Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke paas aaey aur us shakhs ne Sara haal aap se bayan kya wo shakhs zard rang dublaa seedhey baalon wala tha aur jis par dawa karta tha wo par gosht pindliyon waalaa, gandam rang , mota tha. janab Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya Allah to khol de. phir wo aurat bachcha jani jo mushabeh (similar) tha us shakhs ke jis par tohmat thi. tab janab Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne liaan karwaya donon mein. aik shakhs bola aey Ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) ! kya ye aurat wahi aurat thi, jiske liye janab Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya tha agar main kisi ko baghair gawaahon ke sangsaar karta to is aurat ko karta. Ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha nahi wo dusri aurat thi jo musalmanon mein burai ke sath mashhoor thi (yani log kehtey they ke ye faahisha hai na gawah they na iqrar tha) ."
3759,"tarjama dusri riwayat ka wahi hai jo uper guzra . usmein itna zyada hai ke wo shakhs jiske sath tohmat thi mota , sakht ghungariyaley baalon wala tha."
3760,Qasim-bin-Muhammad se riwayat hai Ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) ke samney liaan walon ka zikr hua to Abdullaah-bin-Shaddad ne kaha un hi mein wo aurat thi jiske liye Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya tha agar main kisi ko baghair gawaahon ke rajm (sangsaar) karta to us aurat ko rajm (sangsaar) karta. Ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha : nahi wo aurat dusri aurat thi jo ailaaniya badkaar thi. ibne-abi-Umar ne Qasim-bin-Muhammad se bayan ki hui apni riwayat mein kaha ke unhon ( Qasim ( ne kaha : maine Ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) se suna.
3761,Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai Sad-bin-Ubada Ansari (Raziallahu anhu)) Ansar ke raees ( ne kaha ya Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ! agar koi shakhs apni bevi ke sath kisi mard ko paaey ( zina kartey huey) kya usko mar daaley? Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya nahi. Sad ne kaha nahi mar daley qism uski jisne aapko sachchai ke sath izzat di. Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : (aur sahaba se) suno tumharey sardaar kya kehtey hain. (yani tajjub hai unse ke aisi baat kehtey hain Allah Taala ke hukm ke samney tabiat aur ghussa ko dakhal na dena chahiye ( .
3762,Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai Sad-bin-Ubada (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha ya Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ! agar main apni biwi ke paas ghair mard ko dekhun to kya usko mohlat dun char gawah laney tak ? aap ne farmaya : haan.
3763,Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai Sad-bin-Ubada (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha ya rasoolullah! agar main apni biwi ke sath kisi mard ko dekhun to main usko hath na lagaaun jab tak char gawah na laaun ? aap ne farmaya be-shak . Sad (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha hargiz nahi main to qism uski jisne aapko sachchai ke sath bheja jaldi iska ilaaj talwaar se kar dun us se pahley . Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya suno tumharey sardar kya kehtey hain wo badey ghairat daar hain aur main unse zyada ghairat daar hun aur Allah jalle-jalalahu mujh se zyada ghairat rakhta hai.
3764,"Mughira-bin-Shoba (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai Sad-bin-Ubada (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha agar main apni bevi ke paas kisi mard ko dekhun to talwaar se mar daalun kabhi na chhodun . ye khabar Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko pahunchi aap ne farmaya : tum Sad ki ghairat se tajjub kartey ho, qism Allah ki main unse zyada ghairat-daar hun aur Allah mujh se zyada ghairat daar hai. haram kya Allah ne be sharmi ki baton ko chhipi aur khuli isi ghairat ki wjah se aur koi shakhs Allah Taala se zyada ghairat daar nahi hai aur Allah se zyada kisi shakhs ko uzr pasand nahi hai. usi liye Allah Taala ne paighambaron ko bheja khushi aur dar sunatey huey (taake bandey saza se pahley uski baargah mein uzr kar lein aur tauba karein (aur kisi shakhs ko Allah se zyada tareef pasand nahi isliye Allah Taala ne wada kya jannat ka (taake bandey uski ibadat aur tareef karke jannat hasil kar lein). ,"
3765,"is sanad se bhi ye hadis marwi hai is riwayat main ( , غَیْرَ مُصْفَعٍ , (ke alfaz hain aur) , عَنْہ , ( nahi hai."
3766,Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai aik shakhs bani Fazara mein se aaya Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke paas aur kaha meri joru ko aik kala bachcha paida hua hai (to wo mera malum nahi hota kyonke main kala nahi hun) . janab Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya terey paas oont hain? usne kaha haan hain. aap ne farmaya unka rang kya hai? wo bola laal hai. aap ne farmaya unmein koi khaaki bhi hai? usne kaha haan khaaki bhi hain. aap ne farmaya phir ye rang kahan se aaya? usne kaha kisi rag ne ghaseet liya hoga. aap ne farmaya is bachchey ko bhi kisi rag ne ghaseet liya hoga.
3767,Zohri ne ibne-Uena ki hadis ki manind (tarah) riwayat ki usmein itna farq hai ke kaha aey Rasulullah ! meri aurat ne ladka siyah janaa hai aur mera irada hai ke iska inkar karun aur dusri hadis mein itna zyada hai ke phir Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne iske inkar karne ki ijazat na di.
3768,"Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke aik dehati aaya Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke paas aur kaha aey Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ! meri aurat ne kala bachcha jana hai aur main iska inkar karta hun, to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne usko farmaya terey paas oont hain? usne kaha haan. aap ne farmaya unka rang kaisa hai? usne kaha surkh . aap ne puchha ke unmein koi kala bhi hai? wo bola haan to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ye rang kahan se aa gaya? dehati bola ke aey Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) kisi rag ne ghaseet liya hoga to janab Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke yahan bhi kisi rag ne ghaseet liya hoga."
3769,Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) Nabi akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se isi tarah ki riwayat bayan kartey hain.
